---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Verify Authorized Rentar® Reseller"
  description="Learn how to verify authorized Rentar distributors and protect your investment by purchasing genuine Rentar Fuel Catalyst products."
>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-label">IP &amp; Distribution</p>
    <h1 class="section-title">Verify Authorized Rentar Reseller</h1>

    <div class="manifesto-block">
      <p class="manifesto-highlight">Protect your investment. Verify before you purchase.</p>
      <p>Rentar<sup style="font-size:0.55em;">®</sup> Environmental Solutions maintains an authorized global distribution network to ensure that every customer receives genuine Rentar Fuel Catalyst products backed by factory technical support, current documentation, and applicable warranty coverage. This page provides the tools to verify whether a supplier is currently authorized.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Actions -->
    <div style="display:flex; gap:16px; margin:32px 0; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/downloads/Rentar_Verification_Advisory_Professional.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary" aria-label="Download Verify Authorized Rentar Reseller PDF">Download Verification Advisory (PDF)</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com" class="btn btn-outline">Verify by Email</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com?subject=Unauthorized%20Rentar%20Reseller%20Report" class="btn btn-outline" style="border-color:#c0392b; color:#c0392b;">Report Unauthorized Representation</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Five Questions -->
    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); margin:40px 0 16px;">Five Questions Every Purchaser Should Ask</h2>

    <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
      <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-size:0.9rem;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background:var(--navy); color:var(--white);">
            <th style="padding:12px 16px; text-align:left; width:34%;">Question</th>
            <th style="padding:12px 16px; text-align:left; width:26%;">Purpose</th>
            <th style="padding:12px 16px; text-align:left; width:40%;">Expected Response</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="background:#fafafa;">
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; font-weight:600; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;">Is your company currently an authorized Rentar distributor?</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Establish authorization status directly.</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Yes, with written authorization from Rentar<sup style="font-size:0.55em;">®</sup> Environmental Solutions.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; font-weight:600; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;">Can you provide written proof of authorization?</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Obtain verifiable documentation of authorization status.</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Written authorization letter or certificate from Rentar on company letterhead.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#fafafa;">
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; font-weight:600; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;">Do you source products directly from Rentar?</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Confirm supply chain integrity from manufacturer to end customer.</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Yes, direct supply from Rentar with traceable product documentation.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; font-weight:600; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;">Will my products be eligible for factory warranty and support?</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Protect investment and ensure access to Rentar support infrastructure.</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Yes, all products supplied through authorized channels carry full warranty coverage.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#fafafa;">
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; font-weight:600; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;">Can I verify your authorization status directly with Rentar?</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Independent verification for procurement confidence and compliance.</td>
            <td style="padding:12px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0; color:var(--gray-text);">Yes, contact Rentar at info@rentar.com for authorization verification.</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); margin:40px 0 16px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <p style="font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:4px;">How do I know if a supplier is authorized?</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-text); margin-bottom:16px;">Contact Rentar at <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com">info@rentar.com</a> with the company name and any documentation they have provided. Rentar will confirm or deny authorization status directly.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <p style="font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:4px;">What happens if I buy from an unauthorized source?</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-text); margin-bottom:16px;">Products purchased through unauthorized channels may not be genuine, may not be eligible for warranty coverage or factory support, and may not meet Rentar performance specifications.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <p style="font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:4px;">How do I become an authorized distributor?</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-text); margin-bottom:16px;">Rentar selectively partners with qualified organizations serving industrial markets. Contact <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com">info@rentar.com</a> to discuss distributor authorization.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <p style="font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:4px;">How do I report someone claiming to sell Rentar products without authorization?</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-text); margin-bottom:16px;">Email <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com?subject=Unauthorized%20Rentar%20Reseller%20Report">info@rentar.com</a> with the subject "Unauthorized Rentar Reseller Report" and include the company name, website, any quotations or sales literature, and supporting documents.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:48px; padding:32px; background:var(--navy); border-radius:4px;">
      <h3 style="color:var(--white); font-size:1.2rem; margin-bottom:12px;">Download the Official Advisory</h3>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom:20px; font-size:0.95rem;">The Authorized Reseller Verification Advisory is the official Rentar publication for procurement teams.</p>
      <a href="/downloads/Rentar_Verification_Advisory_Professional.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary" aria-label="Download Rentar Verification Advisory PDF">Download PDF</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
